      "value": "<p>As a standard action, the shaman assumes the form, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.br37848gchetel0q]{Beast Shape IV}, of one of the following animals:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://aonprd.com/MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Dire%20Bear%20(Cave%20Bear)\">dire bear</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://aonprd.com/MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Dire%20Tiger%20(Smilodon)\">dire tiger</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://aonprd.com/MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Mastodon\">mastodon</a>, or woolly rhinoceros.</p>\n<p>The duration of this transformation is 1 hour per level.</p>\n<p>The shaman can use this ability once per day.</p>",
